summary:
Add the outfit of Ronin Japanese style.
For male only.

I am sorry, but I cannot use English.


Description
===========
Adds stand alone Ronin outfit of 7 colors.
And, one feetware.


Location
===============
Use console command \"coc qasmoke\".
The bottom right in closet.
When leaving the room is console command \"coc whiterun\".
